description: Experience elevated living and modern convenience at 84 A St Residences, a boutique building featuring 4 luxury homes located at the intersection of South Boston and Fort Point. The building is being crafted by a prominent local developer known for their attention to detail. This full-floor residence sits on the 3rd floor and offers direct elevator access from the units deeded garage parking space. Inside, you’ll find 2 bedrooms, with ensuite bathrooms and walk-in closets. A flexible bonus room is perfect for a home office or 3rd bed. A half bath adds convenience to the open concept main living area. The kitchen is thoughtfully designed with sleek push to open cabinetry, underlighting, quartzite countertops and a complimenting backsplash. The open concept kitchen and living area flow seamlessly onto a private balcony ideal for entertaining. Additional highlights include a dedicated mudroom, laundry room, oak flooring, oversized windows that flood the space with natural light.
